snippet.title: [MAME] Disney Game It! Classic Pals (c)2006 PDP / Disney / Jungle Soft
snippet.description: A selection of the games you can find in the other SunPlus collections, but with a Disney license and Disney character assets in place of the generic ones.  Interesting product.
